        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee> Editor &amp; Proprietor of “The
                Occident.”</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I herewith send you Extracts from several<lb/> Letters recd from
                    <persName>Mr Cresson</persName> from <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>,
                which<lb/> I recently spoke to you about &amp; which you kindly offered<lb/> to
                insert in “The Occident.” <persName>Mr Cresson</persName> is striving<lb/> hard to
                Establish a school of Agriculture, connecting<add>?</add><lb/> also with the free
                distribution of Food to our poor co-<lb/>=religionists in
                    <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName> and think from his untiring Energy<lb/> and
                practical Agricultural knowledge that<lb/> he will succeed in teaching the
                Israelites<lb/> to become “practical Farmers.” provided he is sus=<lb/>=tained with
                funds for a year or two until it<lb/> becomes firmly established, and a few
                dollars<lb/> from Each congregation or <del>Judicious</del> wealthy<lb/> Israelite
                in the <placeName>U. States</placeName> would establish such<lb/> undertaking on a
                firm basis.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I have received several small<lb/> amounts <del>recently from</del>
                to forward to him<lb/> as contributions to sustain his Agricultural<lb/>
                <del>undertaking</del> Establishment &amp; shall <del>make him a rem</del><lb/>
                <del>-mittance shortly of such amounts as</del> take<lb/> much pleasure in remitting
                any amounts that<lb/> may be entrusted to my care for that purpose from<lb/> any
                benevolent Israelites in the <placeName>United States</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Yours with respect</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">A. Hart</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Philada</placeName>
                <date>June 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Sivan 22d 5614</date>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Editor of The Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
